1. ssh into the instance using -X switch  : ssh -X ubuntu@x.x.x.x
2. start xclock to verify. use jmeter


for amazon linux : 

1.  vi /etc/ssh/sshd_config
	sudo service sshd restart

2. 	install xterm components 
	yum install xorg-x11-xauth xterm

3. 	ssh -X -A ec2-user@<public ip>
	ssh -X ubuntu@<private ip>
